Warren Buffet ( Component Interest )
Know about Rule of 72
Double Time = 72 / Interest rate
Example
Investment amount = 1L
( Returns % ) 6 => 72 / 6 = 12 years
( Returns % ) 8 => 72 / 8 = 9 years
( Post office % ) 6.9 => 72 / 6.9 = 10.4 years
Both give average returns in market
